{"word":"G813 - ἄτακτος - átaktos - at'-ak-tos - Unruly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄτακτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">átaktos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">at'-ak-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unruly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒழுங்கில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"disorderly, out of the ranks, irregular, inordiante"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; <i>unarranged</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>insubordinate</i> (religiously): - unruly.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1296/1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297/1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299/1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004/2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392/392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367/4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001/5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021/5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506/506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292/5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293/5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657/657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812/812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813/813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814/814\">G814</a>"}]}